txt.en: Your careful efforts to not offend and only aid the people of An Shêru earn you a semblance of acceptance among the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Your continued efforts to support An Shêru earns you greater favour with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Neutral with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
You must earn Neutral standing with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
